item.title: The javascript transpile dialectic part 1
item.description: Objective Simple demo code for transpiling to Javascript. Review the setup and configuration for different transpiler engines. Target Audience Java Developers new to modern javascript frameworks and tooling Source Documents gradle wrapper gradle-node-plugin jsweet transpiler TypeScript language TypeScript Declaration File TypeScript type TypeScript namespace ECMA-262 6th Edition ECMAScript 5 Summary Writing high-performance JavaScript is a challenge, many tools and Javascript dialets exist, for new developers the nomenculture can be confusing and npm is Massive.
